1:42:58.004 --> 1:43:03.926
Like she was walking one day
and got hit by a car.

1:43:04.010 --> 1:43:05.304
An accident.

1:43:05.637 --> 1:43:06.805
What?

1:43:07.514 --> 1:43:08.515
An accident?

1:43:08.599 --> 1:43:13.687
