so your family can move on.

1:43:16.357 --> 1:43:17.774
Stop the car.

1:43:18.359 --> 1:43:19.401
Dong-hoon?

1:43:19.485 --> 1:43:20.611
Stop the car.

1:43:21.612 --> 1:43:22.779
